    "content_id":  "3f4b4009-d6ec-47f3-a284-0a382395f91e",
    "description":  "Small employers who have not taken on an apprentice in the last 2 years can access advice and support from the apprenticeship brokerage service.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe apprenticeship brokerage service offers advice and support to employers with less than 250 employees and who do not pay the levy. The service aims to support growth in levelling up areas.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThrough the service, you get one-to-one support from regional experts, known as growth partners. The support is available in several priority sectors and regions in England.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe priority sectors are:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eadult social care\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003econstruction\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edigital\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emanufacturing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe priority regions are:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eGreater Manchester and East Lancashire\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eMerseyside and north-west Lancashire\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eYorkshire\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe north-east\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"eligibility\"\u003eEligibility\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo access support you need to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eoperate in one of the priority regions\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eoffer an apprenticeship in one of the priority sectors\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ehave not had an apprentice start within the last 2 years\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ehave been trading for at least 12 months\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you’re not eligible, find out what support is available to \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.apprenticeships.gov.uk/employers\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ehire an apprentice\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-youll-get\"\u003eWhat you’ll get\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe growth partners can offer a range of support such as:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eproviding impartial advice\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ehelping you to consider the right apprenticeship standard for your business\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003esupporting you to select and work with a training provider\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ediscussing the most effective routes for recruiting an apprentice\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emaking sure you have appropriate management and administrative systems in place\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThey will tailor their support to your needs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-access-support\"\u003eHow to access support\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eContact the relevant growth partner in your region to access support.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eRegion\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eLocal authority areas covered\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eGrowth partner\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eContact details\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003eGreater Manchester and East Lancashire\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eBlackburn with Darwen \u003cbr\u003eBolton\u003cbr\u003eBurnley\u003cbr\u003eManchester\u003cbr\u003eOldham\u003cbr\u003eRochdale\u003cbr\u003eSalford\u003cbr\u003eTameside\u003cbr\u003eWigan\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGreater Manchester Learning Provider Network\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:matthew.l@gmlpn.co.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ematthew.l@gmlpn.co.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003eMerseyside and north-west Lancashire\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eBlackpool\u003cbr\u003eKnowsley\u003cbr\u003eHalton\u003cbr\u003eLiverpool\u003cbr\u003eSt Helens\u003cbr\u003eSefton\u003cbr\u003eWirral\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInstitute for Public Policy Research\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:d.cook@ippr.org\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ed.cook@ippr.org\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003eYorkshire\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eLeeds\u003cbr\u003eBarnsley\u003cbr\u003eBradford\u003cbr\u003eDoncaster\u003cbr\u003eKirklees\u003cbr\u003eRotherham\u003cbr\u003eWakefield\u003cbr\u003eSheffield\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eWest Yorkshire Learning Providers\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:Megan.Graves@wylp.org.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMegan.Graves@wylp.org.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003eNorth-east\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCounty Durham\u003cbr\u003eDarlington\u003cbr\u003eGateshead\u003cbr\u003eHartlepool\u003cbr\u003eMiddlesborough\u003cbr\u003e South Tyneside\u003cbr\u003eNewcastle Upon Tyne\u003cbr\u003eNorth Tyneside\u003cbr\u003eNorthumberland\u003cbr\u003eRedcar and Cleveland\u003cbr\u003eSunderland\u003cbr\u003eStockton\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNew College Durham\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"mailto:Natasha.Francis@newdur.ac.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eNatasha.Francis@newdur.ac.uk\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"mailto:Nicola.Kellett@newdur.ac.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eNicola.Kellett@newdur.ac.uk\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
